programme.desc: Aston Villa is up against Tottenham Hotspur at Villa Park in matchround 28 of the Premier League. The Villans have won three consecutive league fixtures versus Spurs, directly following a run of two victories in 21 league games against them.

programme.title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs. Nottingham Forest : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: Brighton and Hove Albion hosts Nottingham Forest at Amex Stadium in Premier League matchround 28. The Seagulls won 3-2 at City Ground in the reverse fixture this season, despite a red card for Lewis Dunk. Joo Pedro scored a double for the visitors.

programme.title: 2007/08: Manchester United v West Ham United : Classic Match
Premier League Stories
programme.desc: Showcasing the personalities who have shaped the Premier League era with a focus on the stories that resonate with international audiences.

programme.title: Chelsea vs. Newcastle United : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: Chelsea contests Newcastle United at Stamford Bridge in matchround 28 of the Premier League. The Magpies won one of their 28 Premier League away fixtures against the Blues, a 2-0 victory on May 2, 2012. Papiss Ciss scored both goals in that triumph.

programme.title: AFC Bournemouth vs. Luton Town : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: Bournemouth is up against Luton Town at Vitality Stadium in the 2023-2024 Premier League. This game was abandoned at 1-1 earlier this season on Dec. 16, 2023 after Luton captain Tom Lockyer suffered a cardiac arrest in the second half.

programme.title: Fulham vs. Tottenham Hotspur : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: Fulham plays Tottenham Hotspur at Craven Cottage in Premier League matchround 29. Spurs have won seven consecutive league away games against the Cottagers, but they were beaten on penalties at Craven Cottage in this seasons League Cup second round.

programme.title: Premier League Moments
programme.desc: A closer look at the legendary players and teams in the Premier League and their most memorable moments from the top flight.

programme.title: Luton Town vs. Nottingham Forest : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: Luton Town plays Nottingham Forest at Kenilworth Road in Premier League matchround 29. In the reverse fixture at City Ground, Chiedozie Ogbene and Elijah Adebayo scored in the final seven minutes to earn the Hatters a 2-2 draw after they trailed 2-0.

programme.title: Burnley vs. Brentford : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: Burnley hosts Brentford at Turf Moor in matchround 29 of the Premier League. The Bees won two of their 13 league away games against the Clarets: a 3-0 victory in the second tier on March 30, 1935, and a 2-1 triumph in the third tier on Dec. 14, 1996.

programme.title: West Ham United vs. Aston Villa : Premier League Soccer
programme.desc: West Ham United hosts Aston Villa at London Stadium in Premier League matchround 29. The Villans are winless in eight PL away fixtures versus the Hammers, since a 2-1 victory at Upton Park on April 16, 2011 (91st-minute winner by Gabriel Agbonlahor).
